query:
SELECT h.name as hospital, d.name as department, COUNT(*) as doctor_count
FROM doctors doc
JOIN hospitals h ON doc.hospitalId = h.id
JOIN departments d ON doc.departmentId = d.id
GROUP BY h.name, d.name
ORDER BY h.name, doctor_count DESC
LIMIT 20;
